Dear Conference Members,

This is just a reminder that if you haven't sent a Final Registration Form yet for NC-AFM2001, 
the deadline for early registration (Yen 40,000) is July 1, 2001.  If you don't pay by July 1, 2001, 
the registration fee will be Yen 45,000.  To save money, we recommend that you send your 
Final Registration Form by this date.

The attached is our latest version of NC-AFM2001 program.

Also, please visit our web-site
http://www-e2.ele.eng.osaka-u.ac.jp/NC-AFM2001

With regards to the upcoming NC-AFM2001 conference, all presentations requiring the use of multimedia 
should be stored on the presenter's personal computer  which should be brought with you to the conference 
as we will not be supplying PC's.
If it is not possible to bring a computer/laptop to the conference, please advise us and send an 
electronic copy to us as soon as possible so that we can make the necessary arrangements.  
Also, please ensure that you bring overhead slides as a means of backup should all else fail.

In addition all presenter's much supply their respective laptop power supplies during their presentations.  
Also, if you bring your own computer, you must provide your own computer AND powercord that must suit 
a Japan 100V.

Should you have any questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to contact us.

We look forward to seeing you in Kyoto!

Best Regards,



