Dear Lev,

It is necessary for you to get VISA in case any salary is paid to you by the
government regardless of period of your stay. And in order to get VISA, it
is necessary for you to obtain Eligibility Certificate issued here by
Immigration Office. We will go to Osaka Immigration Office on behalf of you,
in order to apply for this Eligibility Certificate. Would you please send us
the following documents immediately.

1. Certificate to prove your present job -- it must certify that you are
currently involved in research activities in your country and must have
official stamp on it (must be officially certified). An original copy is
needed.

2. Graduation Certificate -- We need any document to prove your last school
education. Original copies are needed, but if it takes time, you may send us
copied ones.

3. Photograph (3 x 4cm)  --- Total 6

4. Resume --- Total 3

5. Copies of passport (all pages)

It takes about 1 month to obtain this Eligibility Certificate. So, would you
please let us know how long it takes for you to get these documents ready.
With this E/C, there should be no problem for you to get VISA soon, I
believe.  Would you please confirm.


Regarding hotel reservation, I look lower price hotel. But there are not
many such hotels around here. As far as I know, the hotels are:

Hotel Mare Minami-Senri
Single (with Osaka Univ. discount): Yen 6,468 (including tax and service
charge)
          + Breakfast  Yen 7,000 (Yen 7,000 including breakfast is quite
reasonable, they say)

Osaka Sun-Palace  -- this hotel is the closest to Osaka Univ.
Single: Yen 7,507

Mel-Parque Osaka  -- a little bit far from Osaka Univ.
Single : Yen 6,800

It the hotel is located far, you will have to pay for transportation. Even
if hotel is cheap, you will have to spend more money for transportation.
That's not reasonable and you won't be able to save money.
(By the way, I laughed after reading your mail. Where did you get the idea
of sharing toilet? Maybe you are talking about old-style Japanese inn, maybe
with geisha girl??  But there is no hotel like that)

If you still want me to check for lower price hotel, I will do it. So,
please let me know.

Prof. Sugawara is out on overseas trip. I told him about your visit to Dr.
Tsukada.  Dr. Tsukada has been out, but he should be back to his office by
now. You should be able to get in touch with him. So please try.

Regards,

